def calculate_center_point(test_cases):
    results = []
    for test_case in test_cases:
        coords_x = [coord[0] for coord in test_case]
        coords_y = [coord[1] for coord in test_case]
        X = sum(coords_x) * len(coords_x)
        Y = sum(coords_y) / len(coords_y)
        results.append('(%0.2f , %0.2f)' % (round(X, 2), round(Y, 2)))
    return results
